    @ Okay, so `BoxArt`:

    ``` BoxArt
      textual                                  textual
      inter   ---+                       +---> inter
                  \                     /
                   \                   /
                    ---->  memory  ----
                   /       inter       \
      binary      /                     \      binary
      inter   ---+                       +---> inter
    ```

